for Clio!

1347
01:16:45,557 --> 01:16:49,082
Yay!

1348
01:16:49,126 --> 01:16:51,650
[Kaylie] Here you go, sweetie.
And, uh...

1349
01:16:52,869 --> 01:16:55,698
