1362
01:17:25,858 --> 01:17:27,686
Ah...

1363
01:17:27,730 --> 01:17:30,080
You got me on a good day.

1364
01:17:30,123 --> 01:17:32,778
Sit your asses back down.
Let's get on with this.

1365
01:17:34,127 --> 01:17:35,433
