Sooner or later...

1451
01:21:57,782 --> 01:21:59,915
Not so fast, Miss Thing.

1452
01:21:59,958 --> 01:22:00,916
[groans]

1453
01:22:02,874 --> 01:22:04,789
[grunting]

1454
01:22:06,312 --> 01:22:08,967
